THE TAKEOVER Panel is likely to give a rap on the knuckles to Mitchell
Hutchins Asset Management, a US investment adviser which yesterday belatedly
disclosed 24 transactions in the shares of Spring Ram, the UK kitchens and
bathrooms group.
